- `C:\Users\hp\Documents\EASYSOLVE\resources\views\admin\settings\index.blade.php` (form with `platform_name` + `support_email`)
- `C:\Users\hp\Documents\EASYSOLVE\app\Http\Controllers\School\SchoolSettingController.php` (related per-school settings — persists onto `School` model; included for contrast)
- `C:\Users\hp\Documents\EASYSOLVE\resources\views\layouts\admin.blade.php:234` and `resources\views\admin\dashboard.blade.php:159` (nav links)
