# Admin Panel Enhancements — User Management, Subscription Control, Financial Overview

## Context
The admin panel currently has: dashboard, schools CRUD, plans CRUD, payment requests (verify/reject), and settings.
Three high-priority gaps need filling: user management across schools, subscription lifecycle control, and a financial overview.

## Existing Patterns (from codebase analysis)
- **Controller pattern**: Resource controllers in `App\Http\Controllers\Admin\`, extend `Controller`, filter via `$request->filled()`, paginate 15 with `->appends($request->query())`
- **View pattern**: `@extends('layouts.admin')`, `@section('title')`, `@section('subtitle')`, `@section('content')`
- **Card style**: `bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm`, animate-fade-up with delay-N
- **Status badges**: Color-coded pills with dot indicator
- **Role badges**: purple=owner, blue=admin, cyan=teacher, emerald=student, amber=parent
- **Stat cards**: Gradient top bar + gradient icon container
- **Sidebar nav**: Section headers + `sidebar-link` with `data-tooltip`/`data-nav-text`, active via `request()->routeIs()`
- **Mail pattern**: `Mail::to($user->email)->queue(new MailableClass($model))`
- **DB transactions**: Used for multi-model operations
- **Models**: `$fillable`, `casts()` method, relationship methods, helper booleans (`isActive()`, `isPending()`), accessors (`getFormattedAmountAttribute`)

---

## Feature 1: User Management

### 1.1 Routes (add to admin group in `routes/web.php`)
```php
Route::resource('users', UserController::class)->except(['create', 'store']);
Route::post('users/{user}/toggle-active', [UserController::class, 'toggleActive'])->name('users.toggle-active');
```
No create/store — admins don't create users; schools manage their own.

### 1.2 Controller: `app/Http/Controllers/Admin/UserController.php`
```php
class UserController extends Controller
{
    public function index(Request $request)
    {
        $query = User::with('school')->where('role', '!=', 'super_admin');

        if ($request->filled('school')) {
            $query->where('school_id', $request->school);
        }
        if ($request->filled('role')) {
            $query->where('role', $request->role);
        }
        if ($request->filled('search')) {
            $search = $request->search;
            $query->where(function ($q) use ($search) {
                $q->where('first_name', 'like', "%{$search}%")
                  ->orWhere('last_name', 'like', "%{$search}%")
                  ->orWhere('email', 'like', "%{$search}%");
            });
        }

        $users = $query->latest()->paginate(15)->appends($request->query());
        $schools = School::orderBy('name')->pluck('name', 'id'); // for filter dropdown

        return view('admin.users.index', compact('users', 'schools'));
    }

    public function show(User $user)
    {
        $user->load('school');
        return view('admin.users.show', compact('user'));
    }

    public function toggleActive(Request $request, User $user)
    {
        if ($user->role === 'super_admin') {
            return back()->with('error', 'Cannot modify super admin accounts.');
        }

        $user->update(['is_active' => !$user->is_active]);

        return back()->with('success', "User {$user->full_name} has been " . ($user->is_active ? 'activated' : 'deactivated') . ".");
    }
}
```

### 1.3 Views

**`resources/views/admin/users/index.blade.php`**
- Page header "Users" with subtitle
- Filter bar: search input, school dropdown, role dropdown, filter button
- Table: Avatar+name | Email | School | Role badge | Status badge (Active/Inactive) | Actions (View, Activate/Deactivate)
- Pagination links
- Empty state

**`resources/views/admin/users/show.blade.php`**
- Back link to users index
- User hero card: avatar, name, email, role badge, school link
- Detail grid: School, Joined date, Last seen, Status, Class/Section (if student)
- Action button: Activate/Deactivate

### 1.4 Sidebar nav (in `layouts/admin.blade.php`, Management section, after Schools)
```html
<a href="{{ route('admin.users.index') }}" data-tooltip="Users" data-nav-text="Users"
   class="sidebar-link {{ request()->routeIs('admin.users.*') ? 'active' : 'text-slate-600' }}">
    <svg ...users icon...></svg>
    <span class="sidebar-text">Users</span>
    <span class="sidebar-badge ml-auto text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600">{{ \App\Models\User::where('role', '!=', 'super_admin')->count() }}</span>
</a>
```

