## Feature 3: Financial Overview

### 3.1 Routes (add to admin group)
```php
Route::get('finance', [FinanceController::class, 'index'])->name('finance.index');
```

### 3.2 Controller: `app/Http/Controllers/Admin/FinanceController.php`
```php
class FinanceController extends Controller
{
    public function index(Request $request)
    {
        // Revenue from verified payment requests
        $totalRevenue = PaymentRequest::where('status', 'verified')->sum('amount');
        $monthlyRevenue = PaymentRequest::where('status', 'verified')
            ->whereMonth('verified_at', now()->month)
            ->whereYear('verified_at', now()->year)
            ->sum('amount');
        $yearlyRevenue = PaymentRequest::where('status', 'verified')
            ->whereYear('verified_at', now()->year)
            ->sum('amount');

        // Monthly revenue for chart (last 12 months)
        $monthlyData = PaymentRequest::where('status', 'verified')
            ->where('verified_at', '>=', now()->subMonths(11)->startOfMonth())
            ->selectRaw('MONTH(verified_at) as month, YEAR(verified_at) as year, SUM(amount) as total')
            ->groupBy('year', 'month')
            ->orderBy('year')
            ->orderBy('month')
            ->get();

        // Recent transactions
        $transactions = PaymentRequest::with(['school', 'plan', 'verifier'])
            ->where('status', 'verified')
            ->latest('verified_at')
            ->paginate(15);

        // Pending amount
        $pendingAmount = PaymentRequest::where('status', 'pending')->sum('amount');

        return view('admin.finance.index', compact(
            'totalRevenue', 'monthlyRevenue', 'yearlyRevenue',
            'monthlyData', 'transactions', 'pendingAmount'
        ));
    }
}
```

### 3.3 View: `resources/views/admin/finance/index.blade.php`
- Page header "Financial Overview"
- Stat cards row: Total Revenue, This Month, This Year, Pending Amount
- Revenue trend: simple bar chart using inline SVG/divs showing last 12 months
- Transactions table: School | Plan | Billing Cycle | Amount | Verified By | Date
- Pagination

### 3.4 Sidebar nav (in Management section, after Payment Requests)
```html
<a href="{{ route('admin.finance.index') }}" data-tooltip="Finance" data-nav-text="Finance"
   class="sidebar-link {{ request()->routeIs('admin.finance.*') ? 'active' : 'text-slate-600' }}">
    <svg ...chart icon...></svg>
    <span class="sidebar-text">Finance</span>
</a>
```

